name: Beauty of Taj
description: Taj Mahal is an excellent example Mughal architecture, probably the best. The Taj displays its different moods through its varied shades. It is an enormous mausoleum complex commissioned in 1632 by the Mughal emperor Shah Jahan to house the remains of his beloved wife. It is said that Taj Mahal was constructed over a 20 year period. It is located on the southern bank of the Yamuna River in Agra, India.
